00:15:37.900 --> 00:15:38.800
Who uses it?

00:15:39.250 --> 00:15:44.860
Business owners, bankers, retailers,
investors, and even us as consumers.

00:15:45.280 --> 00:15:46.270
How do we do it?

00:15:46.719 --> 00:15:50.709
By comparing the selling price with
the cost price, and then expressing

00:15:50.709 --> 00:15:52.689
these differences as percentages.

00:15:53.055 --> 00:15:54.765
